challengeName: Hunt your way to the TCO16 India Regionals
detailedRequirements:
Note :: This is a fun challenge. No prizes will be awarded for completing this challenge. 

Welcome to hunt your way to TCO16 India Regionals challenge

TCO16 India Regionals is back again. If you missed the early bird tickets for the event, here is your chance
All you have to do is, solve this simple puzzle, having some quickies to test your logical creativity and you are on the way to the TCO.

First 100 correct submissions will win a ticket for TCO16 India Regionals. 

Check this puzzle below, along with the hints given. You have to fill this puzzle offline and note the values of numbers in circles highlighted.





Down-

1) Lowest palindrome number (non zero) of six digits
2) 20th prime number
4) Sum of even number between 1 to 100
5) Value of 32 + 42 + 52
7) Decimal number 1116 represented as octal
9) Sum of numbers in Fibonacci series starting from 0 to 13

Across-

1) First element of sorted array in ascending order- 19, 83, 215, 17
3) Addition of 00 + 01 in binary makes?
4) Binary 11001 to decimal
6) The fifth magic number in nuclear physics
7) Decimal number 37 represented in Hex
8) Binary value of decimal number 6
10) Number that appears between 86 and 151 in Padovan sequence
finalSubmissionGuidelines:
Submission Guidelines-

1) Complete the puzzle
2) Sum the digits in the highlighted circles
2) Submit the single final number in a text file.

Note :: 
1. This is a fun challenge. No prizes will be awarded for completing this challenge. 
2. Completing the challenge, doesn't gurantee a ticket to the event.
3. All submissions will be evaluated at the end of the challenge.
4.The correct submissions will receive a ticket, till tickets last.
5. Submissions will sorted and evaluated based on their submission timestamp.
